name: Haunting-Sweet cotton-candy Mask
description:
This mask is made by papier and cloth (cotton) mâché.
It is light weight and covers half the face.
The out side is made with layers upon layers of cotton and a few layers of a strong fiber paper over top for a smooth finish. 
It has soft gray leather inside with 3 leather heart accents, for more comfort to the wearer.
10in ribbons in a translucent blue, and lollypop pink are attracted
